"title": "8115: discipleship, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8115",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The state of following Jesus Christ, and serving and obeying him. The NT stresses the privileges, joys and cost of this calling.</p>\n<h2>Discipleship involves learning</h2>\n<h3>Learning from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:45\">JHN 6:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:13\">ISA 54:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:44-Lev11:45\">LEV 11:44–11:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:2\">LEV 19:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:7\">LEV 20:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1-Eph5:2\">EPH 5:1–5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:15-1Pet1:16\">1PE 1:15–1:16</a></p>\n<h3>Learning from Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:29\">MAT 11:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:15\">JHN 13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:20-Eph4:21\">EPH 4:20–4:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:5\">PHP 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:21\">1PE 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:6\">1JN 2:6</a></p>\n<h3>Learning from the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:12\">LUK 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13\">JHN 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:13\">1CO 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17\">EPH 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:16-Eph3:19\">EPH 3:16–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:12\">1PE 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>Learning from other people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:9\">PHP 4:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:10\">DEU 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:1\">DEU 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:12\">DEU 31:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:6\">1CO 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:16\">1CO 4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:1\">1CO 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:17\">PHP 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:7\">2TH 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:9\">2TH 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:11\">1TI 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:4\">1TI 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:14\">2TI 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>Learning to do what is good</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:14\">TIT 3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:14\">PSA 34:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:27\">PSA 37:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:17\">ISA 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:9\">ISA 26:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:11\">3JN 1:11</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ calls people to be his disciples</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:19\">MAT 4:19</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:17\">MRK 1:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:21\">MAT 4:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:20\">MRK 1:20</a> <em>Jesus Christ calls James and John</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:21-Matt8:22\">MAT 8:21–8:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:59-Luke9:60\">LUK 9:59–9:60</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:9\">MAT 9:9</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:14\">MRK 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:27\">LUK 5:27</a> <em>Jesus Christ calls Matthew</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21\">MAT 19:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:21\">MRK 10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:22\">LUK 18:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:43\">JHN 1:43</a> <em>Jesus Christ calls Philip</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:19\">JHN 21:19</a></p>\n<h2>The consequences of discipleship</h2>\n<h3>Following Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:38\">MAT 10:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24\">MAT 16:24</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34\">MRK 8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23\">LUK 9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:27\">LUK 14:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:27\">JHN 10:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:26\">JHN 12:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:4\">REV 14:4</a></p>\n<h3>Serving Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:24\">COL 3:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:25-Matt20:28\">MAT 20:25–20:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:42-Mark10:45\">MRK 10:42–10:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:11\">ROM 12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:9\">1TH 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Obeying Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:31\">JHN 8:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:21\">JHN 14:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23-John14:24\">JHN 14:23–14:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:10\">JHN 15:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:14\">JHN 15:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:3\">1JN 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:22\">1JN 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:24\">1JN 3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:3\">1JN 5:3</a></p>\n<h3>Responding immediately to Jesus Christ's commands</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:21-Matt8:22\">MAT 8:21–8:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:20\">MAT 4:20</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:18\">MRK 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:22\">MAT 4:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:20\">MRK 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:11\">LUK 5:11</a></p>\n<h3>Living for Jesus Christ and not for oneself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:15\">2CO 5:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:7-Rom14:8\">ROM 14:7–14:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:2\">1PE 4:2</a></p>\n<h3>Loving others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:12-John13:17\">JHN 13:12–13:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:9-John15:14\">JHN 15:9–15:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:7-1John4:21\">1JN 4:7–4:21</a></p>\n<h2>Total commitment is required of Jesus Christ's disciples</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:37-Matt10:39\">MAT 10:37–10:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24-Matt16:25\">MAT 16:24–16:25</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34-Mark8:35\">MRK 8:34–8:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23-Luke9:24\">LUK 9:23–9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:8\">MRK 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:26-Luke14:27\">LUK 14:26–14:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:33\">LUK 17:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:25\">JHN 12:25</a></p>\n<h2>The purpose of discipleship is to become Christlike</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:22-Eph4:24\">EPH 4:22–4:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:48\">MAT 5:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:40\">LUK 6:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">ROM 8:29</a> <em>God's purpose in election</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1-Rom12:2\">ROM 12:1–12:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:14\">ROM 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:1\">2CO 7:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:4\">EPH 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:28\">COL 1:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">COL 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:17\">2TI 3:17</a> <em>the purpose of Scripture</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:14-1Pet1:15\">1PE 1:14–1:15</a> <em>a call to holiness</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:5-2Pet1:7\">2PE 1:5–1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2-1John3:3\">1JN 3:2–3:3</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of secret discipleship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:1-John3:2\">JHN 3:1–3:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:50\">JHN 7:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:42\">JHN 12:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:38-John19:39\">JHN 19:38–19:39</a></p>",
